desc: Wholesome Conversions Farm is a Florida Farm specializing in pasture raised chicken, duck, and eggs. We are located in Weirsdale, FL and ship to the state of Florida. Know your farmer and stay healthy. We raise non-gmo, pastured, antibiotic free chicken/ducks for both meat and eggs.

layout.text: Florida's freshest, antibiotic free, non-GMO, pasture raised chicken. Not frozen unless you request it.
